  "text": "Skip to content\nHome\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact Us\nDRIVER\nDriver Access Portal\nJoin or access the ATMP-Courier driver platform, built to make every dispatch smooth, fast, and hassle-free.\nDriver Sign Up\nDriver Sign In\nDrivers connect with ATMP-Courier through our Progressive Web App, built for real-time dispatch. Smart notifications and enforced acceptance windows keep operations predictable, reduce downtime, and get you on the road faster. \nNotes\nLinks open in a new tab.\nWhy ATMP Uses Progressive Web Apps\n\nATMP leverages Progressive Web Apps (PWAs) to ensure consistent business logic across all devices. Updates deploy instantly, no app store delays, so owners and operators maintain full control over live operations.\n\nPWAs deliver real-time push notifications, offline resilience, and secure access while reducing maintenance overhead. This approach minimizes downtime and operational friction, supporting efficiency and profitability for every delivery.\n\nTrusted Solutions, Every Mile\nTrust Saber Tech to handle every delivery with expertise and operational excellence.\nFacebook\n \nInstagram\nQuick Links\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact\nSupport\nAbout\nCustomer Order Portal\nDriver App\nSaber Tech © 2026 • Built on ATMP-core • Owner and operator centric logistics platform.\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms & Conditions\nTranslate »",
